   "source": [
    "13. What can you do to save a programme from crashing if it encounters an error?\n",
    "\n",
    "Ans: In order to save a programme from crashing you must enclose the code in a try clause."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "8c4d9663",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "14. What is the purpose of the try clause? What is the purpose of the except clause?\n",
    "\n",
    "Ans: The try clause will check for the compilation error in the code whereas the except clause will handle the error."
   ]
